Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.12,ef_mainT,,0000,0000,0000,,Za chvíli by měl Rendži dorazit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.54,ef_mainT,,0000,0000,0000,,Dnes mu povím pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.55,ef_main,,0000,0000,0000,,Čihiro...
